"title": "5904: maturity, spiritual",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5904: maturity, spiritual",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The development of Christlike character and behaviour in the Christian through a renewed mind and tested faith.</p>\n<h2>Christlikeness as the goal and model for spiritual maturity</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:13-Eph4:15\">EPH 4:13–4:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:6-Col2:7\">COL 2:6–2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:2\">HEB 12:2</a></p>\n<h2>Marks of spiritual maturity</h2>\n<h3>Spiritual understanding</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2\">COL 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:14\">ROM 15:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:6\">1CO 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:20\">1CO 14:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17-Eph1:18\">EPH 1:17–1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:12-Heb6:1\">HEB 5:12–6:1</a></p>\n<h3>Discernment of God's will and changed behaviour</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:9-Col1:10\">COL 1:9–1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:2\">ROM 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:1-1Cor3:3\">1CO 3:1–3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22-Gal5:23\">GAL 5:22–5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:22-Eph4:23\">EPH 4:22–4:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:9-Phil1:11\">PHP 1:9–1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:3\">2TH 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>Stability</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:12\">COL 4:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:14\">EPH 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:17-2Pet3:18\">2PE 3:17–3:18</a></p>\n<h3>Care for the weaker brother</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:1\">ROM 15:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:1-Gal6:2\">GAL 6:1–6:2</a></p>\n<h2>Maturity is to be the aim of the Christian</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:13-Phil3:15\">PHP 3:13–3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:14\">LUK 8:14</a> <em>a reason for spiritual immaturity</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:1\">2CO 7:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:11\">2CO 13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:11\">1TI 6:11</a></p>\n<h2>The process of maturity</h2>\n<h3>God causes spiritual growth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:6\">PHP 1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:3\">GAL 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:14\">HEB 10:14</a></p>\n<h3>Possessing gifts of ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:11-Eph4:13\">EPH 4:11–4:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:11\">ROM 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>Being equipped by the word of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16-2Tim3:17\">2TI 3:16–3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:4\">ROM 15:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:2\">1PE 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:5\">1JN 2:5</a></p>\n<h3>Persevering through trials</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:3-Rom5:5\">ROM 5:3–5:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:10\">HEB 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:3-Jas1:4\">JAS 1:3–1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:10\">1PE 5:10</a></p>\n<h2>The concern of the pastor is to help others to maturity</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:28-Col1:29\">COL 1:28–1:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:9-2Cor13:10\">2CO 13:9–13:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:19\">GAL 4:19</a></p>",
